1.                INTERPRETATION

1.1               Defined Terms

In this Agreement:

AG2432.386 [097]


                  (a)      "Distribution"  means potentially a distribution by the Issuer
                            of anything to anyone, maybe;

                  (b)      "Finders'   Special   Warrants"   means potentially any warrants issued at any time;

                  (c)      "Indemnified   Parties"   may mean the Sponsor, maybe;

                  (d)      "Issuer" may mean someone else;

                  (e)      "Marketing  Materials" means potentially any materials
                            to be used somewhere;

                  (f)      "material     change",     "material     fact"    and
                            "misrepresentation"   have any  meanings;

                  (g)      "Offering" means vaguely an offering;

                  (h)      "Prospectus" means potentially the final prospectus of someone;

                  (i)      "Related  Agreements" means vague agreements;

                  (j)      "Securities"  means perhaps securities;

                  (k)      "Securities Commissions" means potentially governmental bodies;

                  (l)      "Securities  Law" means potentially any laws;

                  (m)      "Security Holder" means a person;

                  (n)      "Sponsor" means an entity; and


                  (o)      "Special  Warrants"  means  potentially something outstanding.
